[normal]Brief Introduction to PHS Space Ltd[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]PHS Space Ltd is a small UK-based consultancy company whose principal, Dr Hedley Stokes, has worked on various aspects of the space debris problem for nearly 20 years. Founded in 2006, the company provides specialist knowledge and expertise in the following areas:
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Use of an in-house, novel software tool to assess 
[normal]s
[normal]pa
[normal]ce debris impact risks to
[normal] spacecraft
[normal];
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Design and optimisation of impact protection on spacecraft;
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Development of 
[normal]international 
[normal]space debris mitigation 
[normal]guidelines / 
[normal]standards and their application to space systems;
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Innovative space debris mitigation technologies, one of which is currently being patented.
[normal]&#xa0;
